<<narrative>>He's mid-session and waves you in — has a second controller already charged.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "brother">>(not stopping) Come on. I've been in a good lobby for an hour.
(handing back the controller)
You remember how from last time?<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Sort of.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "brother">>(already moving to beside you to help) Okay, so the thing is—
(teaching earnestly, not condescendingly)<</dialog>>`,
                friendship: 3, love: 1
            },
            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/brother/vacation/level2/bedroomAfternoon-" + random(1,3) + ".webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
