(looking at you)
Show me what you've been doing today instead.<</dialog>>`,
                friendship: 3
            },
            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/brother/vacation/level2/bedroomAfternoon-" + random(1,3) + ".webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>He wins something significant — shows you before he even checks the scoreboard.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "brother">>(turning to you first) Did you see that?<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Yeah! That was good.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "brother">>(genuinely excited, letting it show briefly) Three months trying for that.
(collecting himself)
Cool. Okay. Cool.
(still grinning)<</dialog>>`,
                friendship: 3, love: 1
            }
        ],

        talking: [
            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/brother/vacation/level2/bedroomAfternoon-" + random(1,3) + ".webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>He swivels his chair round — game off, actual conversation mode.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "brother">>Can I ask you something? Like, actually ask.
(bracing himself)
Do you think I'm—
(struggling)
Do you think I come across as... difficult? To people who don't know me?<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Not difficult. Guarded, maybe.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "brother">>(sitting with this) Yeah.
(quietly)
That's accurate. I'm working on it.<</dialog>>`,
                friendship: 3, trust: 2
            },
            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/brother/vacation/level2/bedroomAfternoon-" + random(1,3) + ".webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>He brings up something he's been thinking about:<</narrative>>
<<dialog "brother">>I've been looking up game design courses. Like, actual ones. For after school.
(showing you his laptop, briefly)
There are some good ones. I don't know if I'm good enough yet but.
(closing the laptop slightly)
I think I want to try.<</dialog>>`,
                friendship: 3, trust: 2
            },
            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/brother/vacation/level2/bedroomAfternoon-" + random(1,3) + ".webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>He asks for genuine advice — not gaming advice:<</narrative>>
<<dialog "brother">>How do you know when you're actually good at something? Like — good enough that it's not just a hobby?<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>(thinking about it) When you can't stop even when it's hard?<</dialog>>
<<dialog "brother">>(immediately) That's me with the design stuff.
(quietly)
Okay. Yeah. I think I know then.<</dialog>>`,
                friendship: 3, trust: 2, love: 1
            }
        ],

        sibling: [
            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/brother/vacation/level2/bedroomAfternoon-" + random(1,3) + ".webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>He puts on a playlist and doesn't use headphones — plays it for both of them.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "brother">>(working on something) You can stay if you want. I'm just in here doing stuff.
(easy)
I don't need silence when it's you.<</dialog>>`,
                friendship: 3, love: 1
            },
            {
