<<dialog "player">>No. It's not.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "brother">>(back to what he's doing, that's all he needed to say)<</dialog>>`,
                friendship: 3, love: 2
            },
            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/brother/vacation/level2/bedroomAfternoon-" + random(1,3) + ".webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>He shows you something he's been doing in private — a world-building document, sketches, notes for his game idea. He's nervous about it.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "brother">>(handing you the notebook) Don't read too much into it. It's just stuff.
(watching your face as you look)
Is it dumb?<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>(properly looking) No, Jake. This is a real idea. This is something.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "brother">>(a breath he didn't know he was holding)
...Okay.
(taking it back)
I've been doing it for like six months. Haven't shown anyone.<</dialog>>`,
                friendship: 3, trust: 2, love: 2
            }
        ]
